=== You + ME Registry

The Solve ME/CFS Initiative's You + ME Registry is a patient-powered research platform with over 4,200 participants (3,033 ME/CFS, 833 long COVID, 473 controls as of 2021), growing at approximately 72 new registrants per week The mobile app captures longitudinal symptom tracking on a 0--4 severity scale, including pain. The registry is designed to harmonize with other ME/CFS data collection efforts and enables researchers to access de-identified data for analysis.


